      "bookmarkId": "3300055496_23_7282-7314",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "7282-7314",
      "markText": "系着有白色斑点的蓝色领带的男人从后边走过来，朝他的脑袋开了一枪。",
      "totalCount": 1605,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055496&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=7282&rangeEnd=7314",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b532080813ab7c2dg016ce5?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=7282&rangeEnd=7314"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055496_6_10080-10112",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10080-10112",
      "markText": "无效票极少，弃权票也极少，百分之七十以上的选民，投的是空白选票。",
      "totalCount": 1092,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055496&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10080&rangeEnd=10112",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b532080813ab7c2dg016ce5?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10080&rangeEnd=10112"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055496_24_1667-1737",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "1667-1737",
      "markText": "这时候一个盲人问，你听到什么响动了吗；三声枪响，另一个盲人回答说；但是还有一只狗在叫；已经不叫了，大概是因为第三声枪响；很好，我讨厌听狗叫。",
      "totalCount": 616,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055496&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=1667&rangeEnd=1737",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b532080813ab7c2dg016ce5?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=1667&rangeEnd=1737"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055496_17_11639-11688",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "11639-11688",
      "markText": "妻子躺在那帮匪徒身子下面，我受不了，第一年还忍受住了耻辱，但最后实在不能再忍受下去，就分居，离婚了",
      "totalCount": 594,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055496&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=11639&rangeEnd=11688",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b532080813ab7c2dg016ce5?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=11639&rangeEnd=11688"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055496_6_1669-1699",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1669-1699",
      "markText": "只有右翼党代表请求把这一决定写入会议记录，以免日后产生争议。",
      "totalCount": 527,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055496&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1669&rangeEnd=1699",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b532080813ab7c2dg016ce5?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1669&rangeEnd=1699"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055496_21_5350-5443",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "5350-5443",
      "markText": "真正令他吃惊的倒是从镜子里看到的这张脸竟然如此平静，皱纹消失了，一双眼睛变得清澈而且炯炯有神，这是一张五十七岁的男子汉的脸，他的职位是警督，刚刚经受了一场火的考验，如同又接受了一次洗礼。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055496&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=5350&rangeEnd=5443",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b532080813ab7c2dg016ce5?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=5350&rangeEnd=5443"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055496_22_2999-3041",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "2999-3041",
      "markText": "我们出生的那一刻，仿佛为一生签署了一个契约，但可能有一天我们会问自己，是谁替我签署的",
      "totalCount": 430,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055496&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=2999&rangeEnd=3041",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b532080813ab7c2dg016ce5?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=2999&rangeEnd=3041"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055496_11_9047-9102",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "9047-9102",
      "markText": "第三天，或许出于同样的理由，清洁工回到街上来了，没有穿工作服，穿的是普通衣服。他们说，工作服罢工了，他们没有。",
      "totalCount": 420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055496&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=9047&rangeEnd=9102",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b532080813ab7c2dg016ce5?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=9047&rangeEnd=9102"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055496_7_6776-6805",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "6776-6805",
      "markText": "这些人用他们自己的手，并且是不爱国的手，把选票投进了票箱。",
      "totalCount": 416,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055496&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6776&rangeEnd=6805",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b532080813ab7c2dg016ce5?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6776&rangeEnd=6805"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055496_7_792-860",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "792-860",
      "markText": "这几个字还针对各家报纸和社会媒体，他们转眼之间便从欢呼胜利改为落井下石，转变得如此迅速，如此从容，好像从不曾为一场场灾难的诞生推波助澜。",
      "totalCount": 414,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055496&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=792&rangeEnd=860",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b532080813ab7c2dg016ce5?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=792&rangeEnd=860"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055496_6_7547-7620",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7547-7620",
      "markText": "祈求好运的方法多种多样，但几乎全都徒劳无益，而这一种，即强制自己去想最坏的结果，但同时又相信会实现最好的期望，是最为常见的方法之一，值得尝试一下，",
